# Rule Router

Use this map to decide which rules apply to the current task. The **critical reminders** below are also injected at session start by `.cursor/hooks/AIC-session-init.cjs` (single source of truth). **If a rule was not included in context, still follow the conventions below** for that area; read the rule file when you need full detail.

